divs: Sighting DetailsI am sending photos showing something unidentified that I noticed years after the photos were taken. I did not notice anything at the time the pictures were taken, only years later while browsing them. Image-0107 shows something in the sky just above the mountain skyline. Image-0102 shows what could be the same object in the clearing between the trees way above the date stamp. Image-0105 is just for site identification. My female friend was with me when these photos were taken. I have more photos of the area but not cantaining anything unknown.
